  Locus:
    Page: 454
    Verse: 14
Tags:
  - Suffering
---
To live is to suffer; that we suffer is, atleast in large part, our own
fault; thereis a way to eliminate suffering; the wayis open to all; the way
to eliminate suf-fering is to eliminate attachment.
